{"id":8590,"date":"2024-01-28T18:53:23","date_gmt":"2020-04-28T13:23:23","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=8590"},"modified":"2023-04-15T15:49:16","modified_gmt":"2023-04-15T10:19:16","slug":"black-and-white-bathroom-design-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bathroom-interiors\/black-and-white-bathroom-design-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"30 Ideas For The Dreamiest Black And White Bathroom"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>All the black\nand white bathroom inspiration you needed in one place!<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Think of a bathroom and you&#8217;re most likely to picture\nboring white tiles. The thought of a black and white bathroom may seem daring\nat first but that\u2019s exactly what adds to its appeal. This collection of black\nand white bathroom pictures is here to help you visualise the black and white\nbathroom of your dreams. If you&#8217;ve been dreaming of a black and white bathroom\nbut aren\u2019t ready to take the plunge yet, here are some black and white bathroom\ndesign ideas to help you start small.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you&#8217;ve been dreaming of a black and white bathroom but aren\u2019t ready to take the plunge yet, here are some black and white bathroom design ideas to help you start small.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Marble Top<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>For just a hint of a black and white theme in your bathroom, begin with a black marble top around the basin. It works as a lovely contrast in an otherwise all-white bathroom. It may be a small change but the minimalism gives your bathroom a sleek look.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28174605\/marble-top-black-and-white-bathroom-min.jpg\" alt=\"Black and white bathroom design with a black marble top gives your bathroom sleek look\" class=\"wp-image-8614\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28174605\/marble-top-black-and-white-bathroom-min.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28174605\/marble-top-black-and-white-bathroom-min-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28174605\/marble-top-black-and-white-bathroom-min-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28174605\/marble-top-black-and-white-bathroom-min-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Black Elements Bring In Beauty<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Everything white in your bathroom got you feeling bored? Adding black elements is the quickest way to bring in some character! For a speedy makeover to a black and white bathroom, turn to black cabinets and black marble tops.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28175131\/white-bathroom-with-black-cabinets-black-marble-tops-min.jpg\" alt=\"Design your white bathroom with black cabinets and black marble tops to makes beautiful black and white bathroom\" class=\"wp-image-8620\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28175131\/white-bathroom-with-black-cabinets-black-marble-tops-min.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28175131\/white-bathroom-with-black-cabinets-black-marble-tops-min-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28175131\/white-bathroom-with-black-cabinets-black-marble-tops-min-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28175131\/white-bathroom-with-black-cabinets-black-marble-tops-min-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Modern bedroom designs ideas that suit your taste and budget\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/15153814\/modern-bedroom-designs-ideas-that-suit-your-taste-and-budget-scaled.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Black Mirror<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>To get the feel of a black and white bathroom before going the whole way, start small with features like black borders on the mirrors or bathroom cabinets with lovely black and white patterns. Black and white bathroom accessories work as great elements on a white platform as well.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173405\/black-borders-on-mirrors-for-black-white-bathroom-min.jpg\" alt=\"Use black borders on the mirrors or bathroom cabinets for your black and white bathroom design\" class=\"wp-image-8600\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173405\/black-borders-on-mirrors-for-black-white-bathroom-min.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173405\/black-borders-on-mirrors-for-black-white-bathroom-min-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173405\/black-borders-on-mirrors-for-black-white-bathroom-min-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173405\/black-borders-on-mirrors-for-black-white-bathroom-min-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Marble Counter<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>You brush your teeth, groom yourself and probably check yourself out in the mirror over the bathroom counter a million times a day. The bathroom counter is an important but often neglected part of your house. How about giving it an uplift with a patterned black and white marble top?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28175001\/patterned-black-and-white-marble-counter-bathroom-min.jpg\" alt=\"Black and white bathroom design ideas with a patterned black and white marble counter\" class=\"wp-image-8618\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28175001\/patterned-black-and-white-marble-counter-bathroom-min.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28175001\/patterned-black-and-white-marble-counter-bathroom-min-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28175001\/patterned-black-and-white-marble-counter-bathroom-min-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28175001\/patterned-black-and-white-marble-counter-bathroom-min-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Black Marble Top<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A black marble top for your bathroom counter is the first step towards your dream black and white marble bathroom. It rarely ever appears dirty and is super easy to clean!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173522\/black-marble-top-for-bathroom-counter-min.jpg\" alt=\"Black marble top for your bathroom counter to make a black and white bathroom design\" class=\"wp-image-8602\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173522\/black-marble-top-for-bathroom-counter-min.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173522\/black-marble-top-for-bathroom-counter-min-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173522\/black-marble-top-for-bathroom-counter-min-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173522\/black-marble-top-for-bathroom-counter-min-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Black Mosaic Basin<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Think the external basin area in your home is playing spoilt sport to rest of the decor? Give the area a personality by installing black mosaic tiles on the walls around the basin.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173611\/black-mosaic-basin-for-black-white-bathroom-min.jpg\" alt=\"Use black mosaic tiles on the walls around the basin for your black and white bathroom design\" class=\"wp-image-8603\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173611\/black-mosaic-basin-for-black-white-bathroom-min.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173611\/black-mosaic-basin-for-black-white-bathroom-min-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173611\/black-mosaic-basin-for-black-white-bathroom-min-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173611\/black-mosaic-basin-for-black-white-bathroom-min-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Like our designs contact design cafe\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/28144957\/like-our-designs-contact-now.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Black and White Mosaic Tile Bathroom<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Mosaic tiles are usually a popular choice for bathrooms.\nThese black and white bathroom pictures will help your decision-making process.\nSee how smart they look?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Touches Of Grey <\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Introduce some grey in your black and white mosaic tile bathroom. Place a white bathtub right in the centre of your black, white and grey bathroom. Grey blends beautifully with this colour scheme and adds and element of luxury to the space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173129\/black-and-white-mosaic-tile-bathroom-with-grey-touches-min.jpg\" alt=\"Black and white mosaic tile bathroom design with grey touches\" class=\"wp-image-8598\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173129\/black-and-white-mosaic-tile-bathroom-with-grey-touches-min.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173129\/black-and-white-mosaic-tile-bathroom-with-grey-touches-min-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173129\/black-and-white-mosaic-tile-bathroom-with-grey-touches-min-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173129\/black-and-white-mosaic-tile-bathroom-with-grey-touches-min-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Red, Black And White<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>There&#8217;s a whole lot you can do if you have decided on a black and white mosaic tile bathroom. Give your black, white and grey bathroom a pop of colour with this black, white and red bathroom look.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173237\/black-and-white-mosaic-tile-bathroom-with-red-min.jpg\" alt=\"Black and white mosaic tile bathroom design with a pop of colour with red\" class=\"wp-image-8599\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173237\/black-and-white-mosaic-tile-bathroom-with-red-min.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173237\/black-and-white-mosaic-tile-bathroom-with-red-min-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173237\/black-and-white-mosaic-tile-bathroom-with-red-min-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173237\/black-and-white-mosaic-tile-bathroom-with-red-min-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Black, White And Grey<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>This mosaic tiles mix works great when you want a black, white and grey bathroom look. Grey complement both the other shades well and this mix is interesting!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173039\/black-and-white-mosaic-tile-bathroom-with-grey-min.jpg\" alt=\"Mixing grey with black and white mosaic tile bathroom gives great look\" class=\"wp-image-8597\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173039\/black-and-white-mosaic-tile-bathroom-with-grey-min.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173039\/black-and-white-mosaic-tile-bathroom-with-grey-min-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173039\/black-and-white-mosaic-tile-bathroom-with-grey-min-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173039\/black-and-white-mosaic-tile-bathroom-with-grey-min-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Black Mosaic Tiles<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>In more black and white mosaic tile bathroom inspiration, check out this bathroom. All black mosaic tiles across the walls give this space an edgy look.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28172923\/black-and-white-mosaic-tile-bathroom-min.jpg\" alt=\"Black and white mosaic tile walls of bathroom design looks spacious\" class=\"wp-image-8596\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28172923\/black-and-white-mosaic-tile-bathroom-min.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28172923\/black-and-white-mosaic-tile-bathroom-min-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28172923\/black-and-white-mosaic-tile-bathroom-min-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28172923\/black-and-white-mosaic-tile-bathroom-min-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Black and White Subway Tile Bathroom Ideas<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>After mosaic tiles, subway tiles are the next favourite choice for <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/bathroom-design\/\">bathroom designs<\/a>. Take ideas from these black and white bathroom pictures to make sure your space doesn&#8217;t look like just another one with subway tiles.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Black Subway Tiles<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>For black and white subway tile bathroom ideas, how about white subway tiles on one part of the wall and black subway tiles on the other? Go a step further with black and white bathroom floor tiles in a diamond pattern. All white sanitaryware gives this space visual relief too!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173655\/black-subway-tiles-for-black-and-white-bathroom-min.jpg\" alt=\"Black and white bathroom design ideas with black subway tiles \" class=\"wp-image-8604\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173655\/black-subway-tiles-for-black-and-white-bathroom-min.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173655\/black-subway-tiles-for-black-and-white-bathroom-min-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173655\/black-subway-tiles-for-black-and-white-bathroom-min-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173655\/black-subway-tiles-for-black-and-white-bathroom-min-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Black Walls For Your Bathroom Design<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>If the idea of white subway tiles on the entire bathroom wall doesn&#8217;t excite you, get one half of the wall painted a solid black. This is a classic and easy way to incorporate the colour into your bathroom.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173822\/black-walls-bathroom-design-min.jpg\" alt=\"Black walls for your black and white bathroom designs gives you classic look\" class=\"wp-image-8606\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173822\/black-walls-bathroom-design-min.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173822\/black-walls-bathroom-design-min-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173822\/black-walls-bathroom-design-min-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173822\/black-walls-bathroom-design-min-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Black Flooring For Your Bathroom<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Opt for an all-black floor and juxtapose it with white subway tiles on the wall if you&#8217;re looking for black and white subway tile bathroom ideas. Invest in black and white bathroom accessories to add more character to this space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173444\/black-flooring-for-black-and-white-bathroom-min.jpg\" alt=\"Best black and white subway tile bathroom idea with black flooring\" class=\"wp-image-8601\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173444\/black-flooring-for-black-and-white-bathroom-min.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173444\/black-flooring-for-black-and-white-bathroom-min-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173444\/black-flooring-for-black-and-white-bathroom-min-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173444\/black-flooring-for-black-and-white-bathroom-min-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Diamond Patterned Floor<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>In vintage black and white bathroom ideas, a black and white bathroom floor with a diamond pattern is a popular favourite. Keep the walls simple with white subway tiles to allow your bathroom floor to be the hero.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28172619\/black-and-white-bathroom-floor-with-diamond-pattern-min.jpg\" alt=\"Black and white bathroom floor with a diamond pattern gives a beauty in your bathroom design\" class=\"wp-image-8593\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28172619\/black-and-white-bathroom-floor-with-diamond-pattern-min.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28172619\/black-and-white-bathroom-floor-with-diamond-pattern-min-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\