lack walls and floor and contrasted by the white bathtub\" class=\"wp-image-8610\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28174124\/classic-black-and-white-bathroom-design-min.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28174124\/classic-black-and-white-bathroom-design-min-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28174124\/classic-black-and-white-bathroom-design-min-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28174124\/classic-black-and-white-bathroom-design-min-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Black Vinyl Flooring<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Black vinyl flooring with white walls accessorised with an all-black bathtub. It couldn&#8217;t get classier than this! It&#8217;s a favourite in modern black and white bathroom ideas. Don\u2019t you want it?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173742\/black-vinyl-flooring-with-white-walls-for-bathroom-design-min.jpg\" alt=\"Modern black and white bathroom interior design with black vinyl flooring with white walls\" class=\"wp-image-8605\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173742\/black-vinyl-flooring-with-white-walls-for-bathroom-design-min.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173742\/black-vinyl-flooring-with-white-walls-for-bathroom-design-min-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173742\/black-vinyl-flooring-with-white-walls-for-bathroom-design-min-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28173742\/black-vinyl-flooring-with-white-walls-for-bathroom-design-min-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Wall Art Anyone?<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Take your black and white bathroom decor a notch higher with black and white bathroom wall art. See this image and the abstract pattern on one wall? Makes a statement doesn\u2019t it?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28172737\/black-and-white-bathroom-wall-art-min.jpg\" alt=\"Modern black and white bathroom with black and white bathroom wall art\" class=\"wp-image-8594\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28172737\/black-and-white-bathroom-wall-art-min.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28172737\/black-and-white-bathroom-wall-art-min-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28172737\/black-and-white-bathroom-wall-art-min-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28172737\/black-and-white-bathroom-wall-art-min-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Marble Wall<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>A <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/white-marble-flooring\/\">white marble floor<\/a> paired with a black marble wall is all you need for the classic black and white bathroom of your dreams. Mix the interior design with a fair amount of glass for an ultra luxe look!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28175218\/white-marble-floor-black-marble-wall-for-bathroom-design-min.jpg\" alt=\"Modern black and white bathroom interior with a white marble floor paired with a black marble wall\" class=\"wp-image-8621\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/28175218\/white-marble-floor-black-ma